18. Full page layout compare
React
function App() {
  return (
    <div style={{ padding: 20 }}>
      <h1>Hello</h1>
      <div style={{ display: "flex", gap: 10 }}>
        <div style={{ background: "red", padding: 10 }}>Box 1</div>
        <div style={{ background: "blue", padding: 10 }}>Box 2</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
Flutter
class App extends StatelessWidget {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Scaffold(
      body: Padding(
        padding: EdgeInsets.all(20),
        child: Column(
          crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,
          children: [
            Text("Hello"),
            SizedBox(height: 10),
            Row(
              children: [
                Container(
                  color: Colors.red,
                  padding: EdgeInsets.all(10),
                  child: Text("Box 1"),
                ),
                SizedBox(width: 10),
                Container(
                  color: Colors.blue,
                  padding: EdgeInsets.all(10),
                  child: Text("Box 2"),
                ),
              ],
            ),
          ],
        ),
      ),
    );
  }
}
Fast mental mapping

Ye yaad rakhna:

div → Container

render() / component return → build()

display:flex; flex-direction: row → Row

display:flex; flex-direction: column → Column

justify-content → mainAxisAlignment

align-items → crossAxisAlignment

padding → Padding / Container.padding

margin → Container.margin

width/height → width/height

background/border/radius → decoration

grid → GridView

position:absolute → Stack + Positioned

overflow: scroll + map → ListView.builder

flex:1 → Expanded

Biggest mindset shift

React me tum sochte ho:

HTML element + CSS laga do

Flutter me tum sochte ho:

widget ke around widget wrap karo

Example:

React:

<div style={{ padding: 20, textAlign: "center" }}>Hello</div>

Flutter:

Padding(
  padding: EdgeInsets.all(20),
  child: Center(
    child: Text("Hello"),
  ),
)

Matlab Flutter me styling aur layout ke liye nesting zyada hoti hai.

Sabse important learning path

Agar tum React se Flutter seekh rahe ho, to ye order best hai:

Text, Container

Padding, Margin

Row, Column

Expanded, SizedBox

Center, Align

Stack, Positioned

ListView

GridView

StatelessWidget, StatefulWidget

